data.description:
Welcome to the Sycamore Springs! Great community! Great Schools! 
This home features freshly painted 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with an open floor plan.  As you walk in you have an open Living with a 9-foot ceiling, hardwood floor, kitchen, dining, pantry, laundry, half bathroom, sliding door to backyard with new stairs, and 2-car garage access. As you go up the stairs it splits into the master bedroom to the left and 3 other spacious bedrooms to the right. To the left, you find a Huge master bedroom with a vaulted ceiling and a newly tiled bath, to the right you have 3 spacious bedrooms with a common bath. New carpet, updated master bath. Minutes to major Highways I295 & I95!  Seconds to R. Garland Dodd Park at Point of Rocks features a 176-acre with many facilities for outdoor activities. Make an appointment Today!
